Package it.polimi.ingsw.messages.serverMessages.newElement

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    ChangeMessage
    Interface ChangeMessage represents a generic Message containing an updated copy of a view element that is supposed to be sent to the player using the socket.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    NewChest
    Class NewChest is a ChangeMessage that contains an updated copy of a player's chest.
    NewDevDeck
    Class NewDevDeck is a ChangeMessage that contains the updated copy of the first card of a development cards deck.
    NewDevSpace
    Class NewDevSpace is a ChangeMessage that contains an updated copy of a player's development space.
    NewHandCards
    Class NewHandCards is a ChangeMessage that contains an updated copy of a player's hand leader cards.
    NewItinerary
    Class NewItinerary is a ChangeMessage that contains an updated copy of a player's itinerary.
    NewMarket
    Class NewMarket is a ChangeMessage that contains the updated copy of the market.
    NewPlayedLeadCards
    Class NewPlayedLeadCards is a ChangeMessage that contains the updated copy of a player's played leader cards.
    NewPlayers
    Class NewPlayers is a ChangeMessage that contains an the nicknames of all players in the game
    NewWarehouse
    Class NewWarehouse is a ChangeMessage that contains an updated copy of a player's warehouse.
